pageContext.quote: At a certain point in time, you go, “How much fucking sand is left in this goddamned hour glass? What are we doing with it?” You know? Are we on a continued path of improvement and spiritual enlightenment, or do we eventually go, “Hey, guys, there’s a cliff coming up. Let’s just have a drink. There’s a fucking cliff. There’s a cliff right over there. We’re both looking at it.”
